body:
## What's Changed
* fix: remove duplication of checksum  by @owenrumney in https://github.com/aquasecurity/tfsec/pull/1665
* feat(rego): Add --rego-only flag to run rego policies exclusively by @liamg in https://github.com/aquasecurity/tfsec/pull/1667
* fix(rego): Fix code highlighting for rego detections by @liamg in https://github.com/aquasecurity/tfsec/pull/1668


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/aquasecurity/tfsec/compare/v1.17.0...v1.18.0
